# Cloudflare Pages headers.
# Cross-origin isolation is REQUIRED: Open Browser Porter uses SharedArrayBuffer (the
# guest worker, the SAB audio ring, the SAB I/O worker). Without COOP/COEP the
# page is not cross-origin isolated, SharedArrayBuffer is unavailable, and the
# emulator will not start. Range requests (WGB streaming) are served by
# Cloudflare automatically for static assets.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
